Package: alschooldata
Title: Fetch and Process Alabama School Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Al", "Martin", , "almartin@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Downloads and processes school data from the Alabama State Department
    of Education (ALSDE). Provides functions for fetching enrollment data from the
    Federal Report Card system and transforming it into tidy format for analysis.
    Supports data from 2015 to present, with demographic breakdowns by race/ethnicity,
    gender, and special populations.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
